@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Image Editing Operations

actor User
participant "ToolsFragment" as Tools
participant "CropImageActivity" as CropUI
participant "RotateImageActivity" as RotateUI
participant "ImageFilterActivity" as FilterUI
participant "EnhanceImageActivity" as EnhanceUI
participant "ImageService" as Service
participant "Android PhotoPicker" as Picker
participant "MediaStore API" as MediaStore

== Select Editing Tool ==
User -> Tools : Select Image Tool

alt Crop Image
    Tools -> CropUI : startActivity()
else Rotate / Flip Image
    Tools -> RotateUI : startActivity()
else Apply Filters
    Tools -> FilterUI : startActivity()
else Enhance Image
    Tools -> EnhanceUI : startActivity()
end

== Open Image from Gallery ==
note over CropUI, EnhanceUI
Mỗi Activity tự động mở PhotoPicker khi chạy
end note

User -> Picker : PickVisualMedia(ImageOnly)
Picker --> User : Select image
Picker --> CurrentActivity : Return image Uri

CropUI -> CropUI : openInputStream(uri)
CropUI -> CropUI : BitmapFactory.decodeStream()
CropUI --> User : Display image preview

== Crop Image ==
User -> CropUI : Select aspect ratio
User -> CropUI : Adjust width/height sliders
User -> CropUI : Click Apply

CropUI -> Service : cropBitmap(bitmap, targetW, targetH)
activate Service
Service --> CropUI : Cropped Bitmap
deactivate Service

CropUI --> User : Update image preview

== Rotate / Flip Image ==
User -> RotateUI : Rotate or flip image

RotateUI -> Service : applyTransformations(bitmap,\nrotation, flipH, flipV)
activate Service
Service --> RotateUI : Transformed Bitmap
deactivate Service

RotateUI --> User : Update image preview

== Apply Filters ==
User -> FilterUI : Select filter preset
User -> FilterUI : Adjust brightness/contrast/saturation

FilterUI -> Service : applyFilters(bitmap,\ncolorMatrix, brightness,\ncontrast, saturation)
activate Service
Service --> FilterUI : Filtered Bitmap
deactivate Service

FilterUI --> User : Update image preview

== Enhance Image ==
User -> EnhanceUI : Select enhancement option

EnhanceUI --> User : Show processing overlay

EnhanceUI -> Service : applyEnhancement(bitmap)
activate Service
Service --> EnhanceUI : Enhanced Bitmap
deactivate Service

EnhanceUI --> User : Show enhanced result

== Save Edited Image ==
User -> CropUI : Click Save

CurrentActivity -> Service : saveBitmapToGallery(context,\nbitmap, fileName)
activate Service

Service -> MediaStore : Insert image + compress PNG
MediaStore --> Service : Saved image Uri

Service --> CropUI : Return saved Uri
deactivate Service

CropUI --> User : Show success message

@enduml